verbose_text: Although few, if any, studies have reported a GDF mediated mTOR signalling pathway in the central and peripheral nervous systems, the results of the present study are consistent with investigations in mouse fibroblasts and renal fibrogenesis of obstructive nephropathy, in which TGFbeta was shown to be coupled with the PI3K/Akt/mTOR pathway [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
